   - Built up quote premium calculation incrementally through TDD
   - Separated main items from components using `item.type in BASE_PREMIUMS` check
   - Component grouping by type with block discount for exactly 3 alike
   - Item-level surcharges tracked separately, applied per-item not per-policy
   - Policy-level modifiers accumulated into `policyModifiers` variable
   - Claim processing: branched on step.op, stored policies for later claim reference
   - Eliminated duplicate INSURANCE_VALUES map by using PREMIUM_TO_INSURANCE multiplier (10x ratio)
   - Eliminated COMPONENT_INSURANCE constant by deriving from COMPONENT_PREMIUM * PREMIUM_TO_INSURANCE
   - Extracted processQuote and processClaim helper functions for clarity
   - Narrowed processQuote parameter from full scenario to just customer

