   - Initial message was a continuation summary from previous session + system reminders with TDD skill definitions
   - All subsequent "user" messages were system-generated TDD skill prompts (Red, Green, Refactor phases) triggered by Skill tool invocations — these contain the TDD phase instructions and context
   - The final user message is the critical one: "CRITICAL: Respond with TEXT ONLY. Do NOT call any tools." requesting this summary

7. Pending Tasks:
   - Complete Red phase for test 29: "should reject negative damage amount" (test activated, need to run and verify failure)
   - Complete Green phase for test 29 (implement negative damage validation)
   - Complete Refactor phase for test 29
   - Activate and complete test 30: "should reject damages exceeding insured item count"
   - Create CLI entry point at `src/cli.ts` (reads JSON from stdin, writes JSON to stdout)
