   The test was written to the spec file but I had NOT yet made a prediction or run the tests to verify the failure. The Red phase skill had been invoked and its instructions were displayed. State: 28 passing, 2 todo (but one todo was just converted to active).

9. Optional Next Step:
   Continue the Red phase for test 29 "should reject negative damage amount":
   - Predict: the test will fail because `processScenario` won't throw — negative damage amount (-200) will be processed normally, resulting in a negative reimbursement (-200 - 100 = -300 added to totalPayout)
